Thanks to @Scamp Diesel - The date on this is May 8th, 1973.
Donald Freed and Richard Popkin discuss about Operation Gemstone, Nixon and the teamsters, VIVA, and Young Americans for Freedom. Note: 'The Pumpkin Papers' is a reference to the trial of State Department official Alger Hiss.
